candidate for the job 
we are aware that it is inevitable that there will be a period 
where intense disappointment will take over spilman said we 
know that it will not be easily or quickly erased we are convinced 
that given a chance both students and the deaf community at large 
will respond 
zinser received her doctorate in educational psychology from the 
university of california berkeley in 1972 she also has a 
