alakhbar 
when you see they traded and stole and have millions of 
course they used his name people used to be intimidated into 
doing what they wanted some people say he was not responsible 
for his brothers but of course it affects 
esmats trial spotlighted infitah the opendoor economic 
policy that sadat came up with in the mid1970s with its 
loopholes it created many esmats a class of the newly rich 
additionally it created public frustration over the massive influx 
