central bank president fernando milliet 
resigned monday and the government fired the president of the 
semiofficial banco do brasil camilo calazans officials said 
no immediate explanation was given for the dismissals 
milliet the fourth central bank president under brazils 
3yearold civilian regime was in charge of negotiating the 
