experienced banker with the banco do brasil the sao paulo state 
bank banespa and the sogeral bank he is a member of the 
governments national monetary council 
calazans an economist who used to head the governments coffee 
agency reportedly disagreed with finance minister mailson da 
nobrega about wage restrictions for federal employees da nobrega 
favored a wage freeze to reduce the federal deficit but calazans 
nevertheless granted a raise for banco do brasil employees 
calazans was to be replaced by mario gusmao berard the 
secretarygeneral of the finance ministery and closely tied to da 
nobrega 
